00:10:25,134 --> 00:10:27,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five... Four...</b></font>

158
00:10:27,134 --> 00:10:30,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three... Two... One...</b></font>

159
00:10:30,174 --> 00:10:31,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

160
00:10:42,414 --> 00:10:43,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's started...</b></font>

161
00:10:43,914 --> 00:10:46,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stay calm, Takumi.</b></font>

162
00:10:46,854 --> 00:10:50,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shingo purposely eased up on
