166
00:11:11,214 --> 00:11:13,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't be cocky.</i></b></font>

167
00:11:13,284 --> 00:11:16,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The B-16A engine is the best there is.</i></b></font>

168
00:11:16,614 --> 00:11:18,624
