177
00:12:48,344 --> 00:12:51,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but aren't you forgetting something?</i></b></font>

178
00:13:04,524 --> 00:13:07,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Here it goes... it's over.</i></b></font>

179
00:13:32,054 --> 00:13:35,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I pulled it out. I'm lucky.</i></b></font>

180
00:13:35,824 --> 00:13:38,654
