<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, hey, what happened to your enthusiasm?</b></font>

185
00:14:25,374 --> 00:14:27,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't just stand here.</b></font>

186
00:14:27,204 --> 00:14:29,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's follow them!</b></font>

187
00:14:29,874 --> 00:14:31,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think so, Iketani...</b></font>

188
00:14:31,544 --> 00:14:34,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With our skills, we won't catch up with them.</b></font>

189
00:14:34,414 --> 00:14:36,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not trying to catch up with them.</b></font>

190
00:14:36,484 --> 00:14:39,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In case something bad happens to Takumi,</b></font>

191
00:14:39,754 --> 00:14:43,154
