<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, wait for me!</b></font>

193
00:15:47,694 --> 00:15:50,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm getting the hang of this.</b></font>

194
00:16:03,034 --> 00:16:05,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How is he...?</i></b></font>

195
00:16:05,044 --> 00:16:08,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He continues to clear the</i>
<i>corners with little counter.</i></b></font>

196
00:16:08,144 --> 00:16:09,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Unbelievable.</i></b></font>

197
00:16:09,844 --> 00:16:13,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A duct tape death match</i>
<i>can't be mastered instantly.</i></b></font>

198
00:16:13,684 --> 00:16:16,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The safer you try to go,</i></b></font>

199
00:16:16,354 --> 00:16:20,754
